adic (0.9.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * added music by Éric Tremblay
    (one song for the startup menu and one for the game)
  * server now has a list of available levels
    after one game ends automatically selects the next level 
    (--meshURI switch was removed)
  * camera is set on level startup
  * camera rotation
  * client changes music on each level start
  * Éric Tremblay is now the sound designer ;-)

 -- Jens Thiele (karme) <karme@berlios.de>  Sun, 11 May 2003 18:21:56 +0200

adic (0.9.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * minor fixes

 -- Jens Thiele (karme) <karme@berlios.de>  Wed,  7 May 2003 13:42:07 +0200

adic (0.9.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * use dope network byte order stream
  * meta-server now disabled by default
  * server may now report any address to meta-server
  * lag compensation for input events	

 -- Jens Thiele (karme) <karme@berlios.de>  Fri,  2 May 2003 12:01:56 +0200

adic (0.9.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * added TCP_NODELAY option
  * Split into architecture dependent and independent packages.

